summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 4.1°C), outside temperature (down 3.7°C), and inside temperature (down 2.8°C) and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.1 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 232 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 5.7°C), dew point temperature (up 4.2°C), cloud levels (up 402 m), and outside temperature (up 5.3°C) when compared to today.

summary.summary: Inside; temperature should remain cool. Outside; prepare for cold, chilly weather ahead. Also, dry and less humid conditions and winds will be practically absent. Possible light showers, the sky will be mostly cloudy (or even foggy) with low clouds, and it’s dim outside. Low pressure may bring unsettled weather.
